    <stitle>CAM AIR FOUNDATION BRAKES - CLEANING AND INSPECTION - BRAKE SHOE RETURN SPRINGS</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="clean" graphiccount="0">
        <title>BRAKE SHOE RETURN SPRINGS</title>
        <para>Inspect brake shoe return springs for distortion such as nicks, twisted shanks or spread coils. Damaged
            springs must be replaced. It is recommended that the return spring be replaced whenever the shoes or linings
            are replaced.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
